{"tid":2192370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"穆斯林戰士被女兵殺上不了天堂　印度用女兵防巴基斯坦串連中國偷襲","createTime":"2020-09-07T05:28:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T06:21:58.000Z","uid":261647,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ceccd616429751b79a543e51cdbbf8d374ba17f1","tid":2192370,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:28:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=105906477918151&amp;id=105891764586289\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D105906477918151%26id%3D105891764586289&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp4PST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=27cbb17f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=105906477918151&amp;id=105891764586289</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ShUYVsh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FShUYVsh.jpg&h=83252f01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n2MkpkE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn2MkpkE.jpg&h=e1e6c71f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：India Today Insight 今日印度通訊<br />\n<br />\n穆斯林戰士一旦被女兵擊殺的話會導致他們上不了天堂。正因如此，印度最近在跟穆斯林國家巴基斯坦爭奪的克什米爾（Kashmir）地區中部署了來自阿蕯姆地區（Assam）的女兵，以防巴基斯坦串連中國對印度又一次製造邊境矛盾。"},{"pid":"9c92fb69caf596ccbe744a13c3004db0194df8f0","tid":2192370,"uid":226955,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:30:53.000Z","msg":"寫呢套宗教理論嘅人唔知係咪弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無啦啦要整個弱點出嚟比對家，對家一用女兵你地就唔敢打啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd06c2474138f97b99e5352e3e1a9502bc6c9d15","tid":2192370,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:55:08.000Z","msg":"射死班支那巴鐵豬"},{"pid":"8ad3dc1faecb456c7caf27f139e3b9ea0ad81e68","tid":2192370,"uid":158270,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9c92fb69caf596ccbe744a13c3004db0194df8f0","tid":21923